</richcontent><edge COLOR="#DC322F" /></node><node ID="B321AF0D-F556-40DB-BB77-B4FF858465ED" TEXT="Mechanical Requirements" STYLE="bubble" FOLDED="false" CREATED="1561213946000" MODIFIED="1561213971000"><font SIZE="14" /><edge COLOR="#DC322F" /></node></node><node ID="4649F7CD-A9DA-40F2-8846-B5F5C7F5D849" TEXT="Production" STYLE="bubble" FOLDED="false" CREATED="1561131483000" MODIFIED="1561131488000"><font SIZE="14" /><edge COLOR="#DC322F" /><node ID="9A02DF54-73D4-4DBE-9769-3BDE717A87FB" TEXT="Packaging" STYLE="bubble" FOLDED="false" CREATED="1561213721000" MODIFIED="1561213725000"><font SIZE="14" /><edge COLOR="#DC322F" /></node><node ID="843FBC20-A6ED-4038-99F6-131E4219A298" TEXT="Pricing" STYLE="bubble" FOLDED="false" CREATED="1561213727000" MODIFIED="1561216639000"><font SIZE="14" /><richcontent TYPE="NOTE"><html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
<head>


<title></title>
</head>
<body>
<p>The educational bot cost is parcelled with the course price. So
students buy the course and get the bot + shipping included in the
price =&gt; One bundle price for all.<br />
<br /></p>
<p>Customers that decide that they just want the bot and not the
education will pay a &#x201c;markup fee&#x201d; (internal, not visible to user)
so as to fund other parts of our business. Target price is: USD
600</p>
</body>
</html>
</richcontent><edge COLOR="#DC322F" /><node ID="82B5EC4E-3A10-4343-9E52-BC3F8F9B3A05" TEXT="Cost" STYLE="bubble" FOLDED="false" CREATED="1561213611000" MODIFIED="1561215875000"><font SIZE="14" /><richcontent TYPE="NOTE"><html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
<head>


<title></title>
</head>
<body>
<p>Max cost: USD 270</p>
</body>
</html>
</richcontent><edge COLOR="#DC322F" /><node ID="1AC79B7C-FFCC-4604-9A28-A942F166089A" TEXT="Labour Cost" STYLE="bubble" FOLDED="false" CREATED="1561215789000" MODIFIED="1561217666000"><font SIZE="14" /><richcontent TYPE="NOTE"><html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
<head>


<title></title>
</head>
<body>
<p>Labour:</p>
<ul>
<li>Print Plastic Parts</li>
<li>Assemble Plastic Parts</li>
<li>Add sensors</li>
<li>Add Pi + power</li>
<li>Software Installation</li>
<li>Testing</li>
<li>Print User Manual</li>
<li>Package</li>
</ul>
<br />
<p>The plan is to manufacture one bot and go through the steps
above. Iterate and improve as necessary, probably a maximum of 3
times should be enough. Gather data on how long it took, average it
out and come up with &#x201c;Time to Produce Bot&#x201d;. That number is for 1
bot only. We will assume that mass production time is 50% of the
time needed to produce 1 bot.<br />
Minimum wage for labour =~ CAD15/hour</p>
</body>
</html>
</richcontent><edge COLOR="#DC322F" /></node><node ID="3471CE0E-FFC3-4AAD-B07B-4C6707367E48" TEXT="Material Cost" STYLE="bubble" FOLDED="false" CREATED="1561215917000" MODIFIED="1561215940000"><font SIZE="14" /><edge COLOR="#DC322F" /></node><node ID="E856FD8A-10D1-47C1-A637-827C1FBE4F68" TEXT="Shipping Costs" STYLE="bubble" FOLDED="false" CREATED="1561216166000" MODIFIED="1561216171000"><font SIZE="14" /><edge COLOR="#DC322F" /></node></node><node ID="569EBA55-DA43-4DFA-8EF4-01BC1B624C2D" TEXT="Profit Margin" STYLE="bubble" FOLDED="false" CREATED="1561215028000" MODIFIED="1561216780000"><font SIZE="14" /><richcontent TYPE="NOTE"><html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
<head>


<title></title>
</head>
<body>
<p>Margin for Education Bundle is 50%<br />
Margin for customers not interested in education is 100%</p>
</body>
</html>
